<subSubSection pageId="21" pageNumber="619" type="activity">
<paragraph blockId="21.[1360,2567,2530,3312]" pageId="21" pageNumber="619">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1360,1600,3041,3075]" pageId="21" pageNumber="619">Activity patterns.</emphasis>
The East African Gerbil is probably nocturnal and terrestrial like congeners. It digs complex burrows.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
